data.description: Welcome home to this meticulously kept 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home! Upon entering you are greeted by a formal dining and family room that is perfect for the upcoming holidays. The open concept floor plan allows for conversation flow from the large island kitchen, to the dining area to the living room! With all bedrooms located upstairs you'll be able to enjoy peaceful evenings in the extra-large primary suite with dual vanities and closets for the right amount of personal space. The backyard is an entertainers delight with a large pergola perfect for gathering around just in time for Sunday football and barbecues. *Roof was replaced in January of 2022 and A/C was replaced in March of 2023* Schedule your tour today to see your future home!
